&lt;h1 id="what-kate-saw-in-silicon-valley"&gt;What Kate Saw in Silicon Valley&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;August 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kate Courteau is the architect who designed Y Combinator&amp;rsquo;s office. Recently we managed to recruit her to help us run YC when she&amp;rsquo;s not busy with architectural projects. Though she&amp;rsquo;d heard a lot about YC since the beginning, the last 9 months have been a total immersion.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>